OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1780427467
OL,3,CPolice recruits trained on-island for
OL,4,Cthe first time in a decade
OL,6,FStudent police officers, trained on-
OL,7,Fisland for the first time in more than
OL,8,Fa decade, have qualified to join
OL,9,FJersey's force.
OL,11,FThe ten constables who passed out on
OL,12,FFriday, were part of a 20-week
OL,13,Fprogramme, that the States of Jersey
OL,14,FPolice says saved #150,000.
OL,16,FIt's a move away from student officer
OL,17,Ftraining in Norfolk, which required 10
OL,18,Fweeks of travel and a further three
OL,19,Fweeks on-island focused on Jersey law
OL,20,Fspecifics.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1780427467
OL,3,CPolice recruits trained on-island for
OL,4,Cthe first time in a decade
OL,6,FOne of the new officers says anyone
OL,7,Fcan join but believes the police
OL,8,Fvalues aligned with his personal
OL,9,Fstrengths.
OL,11,FPolice Constable Lewis Wynne says:
OL,12,F"It's been a long, sometimes hard, but
OL,13,Fbrilliant road. We've learnt a lot
OL,14,Fabout ourselves.
OL,16,F"We started with 10 and ended with 10.
OL,17,FThe people on this course have been
OL,18,Famazing. Everyone has pulled each
OL,19,Fother through. Mistakes are when you
OL,20,Flearn the most out of it."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1780427467
OL,3,CPolice recruits trained on-island for
OL,4,Cthe first time in a decade
OL,6,FThere are warnings from those in
OL,7,Fcharge that the new constables will
OL,8,Fneed to adapt their policing
OL,9,Ftechniques to tackle advancing
OL,10,Ftechnology.
OL,12,FJersey's Chief of Police, Robin Smith
OL,13,Fsays: "Criminals are the most
OL,14,Fentrepreneurial bunch you'll ever
OL,15,Ffind. They don't need to stick to
OL,16,Frules, they don't pay taxes, they can
OL,17,Ffind all different ways to diversify.
OL,19,F"What the police service must do is
OL,20,Fdiversify as well. Be legally
OL,21,Faudacious, sometimes ruthless."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1780427467
OL,3,CPolice recruits trained on-island for
OL,4,Cthe first time in a decade
OL,6,FHe added: "When I joined the police
OL,7,Fservice there was no internet, there
OL,8,Fwas no artificial intelligence.
OL,10,F"Technology is moving even quicker, so
OL,11,Fwe need to make sure in order to keep
OL,12,Fislanders safe, we are agile, as agile
OL,13,Fas criminals, particularly those doing
OL,14,Fscams on phones. I'm very confident we
OL,15,Fcan do that."
OL,17,FThe training will be rolled out again
OL,18,Fin Jersey for the next intake in
OL,19,FJanuary 2027.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1780427467
OL,3,CPolice recruits trained on-island for
OL,4,Cthe first time in a decade
OL,6,FForce Development Manager, Paul Smith
OL,7,Fsays: "We are immensely proud of what
OL,8,Fthey've achieved. They've looked at
OL,9,Feverything a police officer needs on
OL,10,Fthe island of Jersey and passed a
OL,11,Fnumber of hard exams.
OL,13,F"In a weeks time, they will be going
OL,14,Fout with their tutors and with the
OL,15,Fpublic to learn their craft of
OL,16,Fpolicing."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
